shorkie-pytorch
Copyright 2025 Timon Schneider

This project is a PyTorch reimplementation of the Shorkie model, originally
developed in TensorFlow/Keras. The model architecture and training methodology
are based on the following work:

  Shorkie: a yeast sequence-to-expression model
  Chao et al.
  https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2025.09.19.677475v1

The original TensorFlow implementation is available at:
  https://github.com/calico/shorkie-paper (Apache-2.0)
  https://github.com/calico/baskerville-yeast (Apache-2.0)

